.RE
.SH "FILE LOCATION"
.sp
Place \fB.gitcommitizen\fP in the root of a Git repository.
.SH "NOTES"
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.  sp -1
.  IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
Section names (\f(CR[settings]\fP, \f(CR[scopes]\fP, \f(CR[types]\fP) are case\-insensitive.
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.  sp -1
.  IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
Types are lowercase identifiers (e.g., \f(CRfeat\fP, \f(CRfix\fP).
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.  sp -1
.  IP \(bu 2.3
.\}
Scopes may include letters, numbers, dashes, underscores, and \f(CR@\fP (e.g., \f(CR@types/node\fP).
.RE
